data.description: A place for everyone in this 3,000 square foot home! Open first floor to enjoy family time, including a dining room, office/sitting room, and a 465 square foot TV room/Bonus Room/Play room. All 6 bedrooms are located upstairs, 6th bedroom could also be an office or bonus room/craft room. Large soaker tub in master suite to enjoy relaxing nights in. Home is dual zoned with 2 AC units/2 furnaces. Roof is only 3 years old.
